{"tid":2464083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科興第二針開打 千人甩底","createTime":"2021-03-27T07:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:23:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"12b394dbb28e004049130f6ac4dda488e1630d3f","tid":2464083,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210327/CO6VAH2SEJHB3DJZK5QWDEC4ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210327%2FCO6VAH2SEJHB3DJZK5QWDEC4ZU%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr35S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=caf0e8f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210327%2FCO6VAH2SEJHB3DJZK5QWDEC4ZU%2F&h=b0ca4399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210327/CO6VAH2SEJHB3DJZK5QWDEC4ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n科興第二針開打 千人甩底<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國產科興疫苗接種計劃上月26日正式開始，根據相隔28天打第二針的原則，昨是公眾打二針科興疫苗的日子，但根據政府公佈數字，有1,000人、15%接種者未有如期接種第二劑。未知大量甩底是否與九宗注射科興後死亡個案有關，昨日接種第二劑科興的醫管局前主席梁智鴻則「希望市民理性啲」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「小一好淒涼」校長稱先復課<br />\n<br />\n疫苗接種計劃首天，即2月26日當日有6,000人接種科興疫苗。根據政府顧問專家委員會建議，第一劑和第二劑科興疫苗應相隔28日接種，因此昨日應有6,000人接種第二劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6FOkyJgkvma2PdvHXRinUraJq5o=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UEB3EHGNG5CUDMJ2KKHQQQIPSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6FOkyJgkvma2PdvHXRinUraJq5o%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUEB3EHGNG5CUDMJ2KKHQQQIPSY.jpg&h=74e0c567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■醫管局前主席梁智鴻（左）昨到中央圖書館接種中心注射第二劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁智鴻：希望市民理性<br />\n<br />\n然而，昨日政府公佈數字顯示，全日只有5,100人接種第二劑科興疫苗，當中約4,900人在社區疫苗接種中心接種，約200人是在私家醫生和診所接種。換言之，有900人未有如期於昨日接種第二劑科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：打復必泰3日「以為副作用」<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，28日前，累計超過6,600人接種了第一劑科興疫苗，但截至昨日，累積接種兩劑科興疫苗的人數也只得5,600人，有1,000人未有如期接種。<br />\n<br />\n上月底開打的科興疫苗事故頻生，至今九人注射後死亡，亦有接種者出現面癱、無法步行等嚴重副作用。在中央圖書館疫苗接種中心，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現年67歲的市民吳先生昨接種第二針，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一名不願具名的男士前來打第一針，。。。。。"},{"pid":"0e26ae7fe6656f86d36eb47373410e79dcc748c8","tid":2464083,"uid":39492,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"依家甩底唔打就叫唔理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死咗幾件、面癱咗幾件, 一件打完照中<br />\n仲去打嘅先叫唔理性喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b977e63446029be1cc6ed23adb4d8ac294c7a2","tid":2464083,"uid":49329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"藍屍更加貪生怕死"},{"pid":"06d745048cc43e03175dcfae1a87f4c41edfdf82","tid":2464083,"uid":13872,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"其實行過見到都有唔少後生排隊打，其實連登係咪係同溫層"},{"pid":"e3508da8e51da1139602a6891ae2b877242c29b8","tid":2464083,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f7474731a36c902976aecfde91e390f42364e7","tid":2464083,"uid":89161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147bc91048ea31f1457fb7be0de84a8a329d8fd7","tid":2464083,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7c572c3d8a28a6ff66bb88501c5def97598932","tid":2464083,"uid":254745,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"06d745048cc43e03175dcfae1a8